'''1889–1890年流感大流行'''（{{lang-en|1889–1890 flu pandemic}}），又称“'''俄国流感'''（Russian flu）”，是指于1889年[[疾病爆发|爆发]]的一次[[流感大流行|流感大流行]]。<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=The influenza epidemic of 1889–90 in selected European cities – a picture based on the reports of two Poznań daily newspapers from the second half of the nineteenth century|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3867475/|last=Kempińska-Mirosławska|first=Bogumiła|last2=WoŸniak-Kosek|first2=Agnieszka|date=2013-12-10|journal=Medical Science Monitor : International Medical Journal of Experimental and Clinical Research|doi=10.12659/MSM.889469|volume=19|pages=1131–1141|issn=1234-1010|pmc=3867475|pmid=24322721|accessdate=2020-12-15|archivedate=2021-01-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118084418/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3867475/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=An uncommon cold|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7252012/|last=King|first=Anthony|date=2020-05-02|journal=New Scientist (1971)|issue=3280|doi=10.1016/S0262-4079(20)30862-9|volume=246|pages=32–35|issn=0262-4079|pmc=7252012|pmid=32501321|accessdate=2020-12-15|archivedate=2021-01-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107031114/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7252012/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite journal|title=Origins of the Spanish Influenza pandemic (1918–1920) and its relation to the First World War|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2805838/|last=Erkoreka|first=Anton|date=2009-11-30|journal=Journal of Molecular and Genetic Medicine : An International Journal of Biomedical Research|issue=2|volume=3|pages=190–194|issn=1747-0862|pmc=2805838|pmid=20076789|accessdate=2020-12-15|archivedate=2021-01-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120151554/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2805838/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=1889年俄国流感4个月席卷全球 百万人丧生|url=http://news.sohu.com/20130414/n372619686.shtml|accessdate=2020-12-15|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=[[新华网|新华网]]|agency=[[搜狐|搜狐]]|language=|archivedate=2016-09-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921012419/http://news.sohu.com/20130414/n372619686.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=1889年，俄国流感4个月席卷全球|url=http://gb.oversea.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?filename=XSHD201305025&dbcode=CJFD&dbname=CJFDTEMP|accessdate=2020-12-15|author=葛元芬|publisher=中国期刊全文数据库}}</ref> 最主要的一波疫情发生于1889年-1890年，此后1890年-1892年又发生了两波较大规模的疫情。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":4">{{Cite journal|title=A brief outline of respiratory viral disease outbreaks: 1889–till date on the public health perspectives|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7466926/|last=Noor|first=Rashed|last2=Maniha|first2=Syeda Muntaka|date=2020-09-02|journal=VirusDisease|doi=10.1007/s13337-020-00628-5|pages=1–9|issn=2347-3584|pmc=7466926|pmid=32905186|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2021-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211120024538/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC7466926/}}</ref>此次大流行共造成了全球约100万人死亡，是历史上[[流行病列表|致死人数最多的流行病之一]]，也是十九世纪最严重的疫情之一。<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Age-specific excess mortality patterns and transmissibility during the 1889–1890 influenza pandemic in Madrid, Spain|url=https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1047279717306841|last=Ramiro|first=Diego|last2=Garcia|first2=Sara|date=2018-05|journal=Annals of Epidemiology|issue=5|doi=10.1016/j.annepidem.2017.12.009|volume=28|pages=267–272|language=en|last3=Casado|first3=Yolanda|last4=Cilek|first4=Laura|last5=Chowell|first5=Gerardo|access-date=2021-01-31|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111133632/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1047279717306841}}</ref>

1889年5月，该病最早在[[俄罗斯帝国|俄罗斯帝国]]位于[[中亚|中亚]]地区的[[布哈拉|布哈拉]]被发现，与此同时[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[格陵兰|格林兰岛]]等地也有疫情报告。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":4" /> 俄国当地的大规模铁路建设加重了疫情。<ref name=":0" /> 1889年10月，该流感传播到了[[圣彼得堡|圣彼得堡]]、[[莫斯科|莫斯科]]，并沿着铁路线传播到了[[歐洲大陸|欧洲大陆]]。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":5">{{Cite journal|title=Transmissibility and geographic spread of the 1889 influenza pandemic|url=https://www.pnas.org/content/107/19/8778|last=Valleron|first=Alain-Jacques|last2=Cori|first2=Anne|date=2010-05-11|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|issue=19|doi=10.1073/pnas.1000886107|volume=107|pages=8778–8781|language=en|issn=0027-8424|pmid=20421481|last3=Valtat|first3=Sophie|last4=Meurisse|first4=Sofia|last5=Carrat|first5=Fabrice|last6=Boëlle|first6=Pierre-Yves|accessdate=2020-12-15|archivedate=2021-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114061139/https://www.pnas.org/content/107/19/8778|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1890年初，流感传播到了[[美国|美国]]，[[纽约|纽约]]、[[波士顿|波士顿]]等地相继爆发疫情，共造成约13000名美国人死亡。<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":6">{{Cite news|title=Our Coronavirus Predicament Isn't All That New|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-05-15/coronavirus-of-today-eerily-similar-to-1889-russian-flu-pandemic|newspaper=Bloomberg.com|date=2020-05-15|accessdate=2020-12-15|language=en|archivedate=2021-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114055728/https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2020-05-15/coronavirus-of-today-eerily-similar-to-1889-russian-flu-pandemic|dead-url=no}}</ref>

该病的致病病原不明确， 有研究认为是H2N2流感病毒<ref name=":4" /><ref name=":7">{{Cite journal|title=Complete Genomic Sequence of Human Coronavirus OC43: Molecular Clock Analysis Suggests a Relatively Recent Zoonotic Coronavirus Transmission Event|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC544107/|last=Vijgen|first=Leen|last2=Keyaerts|first2=Els|date=2005-2|journal=Journal of Virology|issue=3|doi=10.1128/JVI.79.3.1595-1604.2005|volume=79|pages=1595–1604|issn=0022-538X|pmid=15650185|last3=Moës|first3=Elien|last4=Thoelen|first4=Inge|last5=Wollants|first5=Elke|last6=Lemey|first6=Philippe|last7=Vandamme|first7=Anne-Mieke|last8=Van Ranst|first8=Marc|accessdate=2020-12-15|archivedate=2021-01-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114055607/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC544107/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，有研究认为是H3N8流感病毒<ref name=":5" />，也有研究人员认为俄国流感可能是[[人類冠狀病毒OC43|OC43冠状病毒]]造成的<ref>{{Cite web|title=COVID-19可能會永遠與我們共存，本文告訴你我們會怎麼與它一起生活|url=https://www.natgeomedia.com/science/article/content-12846.html|accessdate=2021-02-02|work=國家地理雜誌中文網|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228161422/https://www.natgeomedia.com/science/article/content-12846.html}}</ref><ref name=":6" /><ref name=":7" />。

